 on the screen that reads, \\\"Update on the Olympic cardboard beds.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first word that came out of her mouth this morning.\\\"\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the video progresses, the athlete is seen complaining about the beds.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The video also shows a snippet from a clip posted by Australian water polo player Tilly Kearns.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"score\": 0.9999839567560691, \"rank\": 1.554346127709544e-05, \"text\": \"Kearns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There, she reveals that the Olympians from her country at the2024 Paris Olympicshave received mattress toppers to make sleeping on hard beds easier.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999651692921, \"rank\": 3.4830716048441216e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by SNOOZ (@snooz)  With over 3.6 million views, the video has gone viral on social media.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has also sparked outrage among people, with many asking how athletes are supposed to perform well if they are unable to have a peaceful sleep.\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Can you imagine the kind of performance we would get from athletes if they actually got a proper night's sleep now?\\\"\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {